              <p align="center"><img src="http://www.my-modellbau.com/images/1_TMB/Bilder/fzk_09.jpg" width="650" height="345" align="center" hspace="6" alt="Image" /></p>
              <p align="center"><font color="#3333CC" size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><img src="http://www.my-modellbau.com/images/1_TMB/Bilder/fzk_0a.jpg" width="650" height="345" align="center" hspace="6" alt="Image" /><br>
                Sie erhalten das Modell komplett und flugfertig (10 Minuten Arbeitsaufwand).</strong> 
                </font></p>
              <p align="justify"> &nbsp;<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><br>
                Technische Neuerungen:</strong></font><br>
                <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Der 
